cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using these metadata."
title: "A Multiple Correspondence Analysis Approach to Mitigate the Non-Communicable Disease (NCD) Epidemic: Introducing a Health-Related Behavior-Based NCD Vulnerability Index"
abstract: >-
  Analysis code for constructing and validating an NCD Vulnerability Index
  (NCDVI) for hypertension in Bangladesh, built from BDHS 2017-18 data using
  multiple correspondence analysis and multilevel logistic regression, with
  TRIPOD-compliant internal validation, decision curve analysis, and external
  validation on BDHS 2022. The repository contains analysis code only; the BDHS
  microdata must be obtained from The DHS Program under its Data Use Agreement.
type: software
